# LiNKagentzero (link-agent-zero) Foundation

LiNKtrend fork of **Agent Zero**: Python **execution** agent framework with plugins, tools, web UI, and skills compatible with the SKILL.md ecosystem.

## Layout

- `python/` — core runtime and helpers
- `plugins/` — bundled and custom plugins
- `docs/` — setup, architecture, developer guides
- `webui/` — frontend when present

## Role

- Terminal and tool execution plane—do not fold orchestration (Paperclip) or channel gateway (OpenClaw) responsibilities here.
